                     <summary>Fragments of Genesis, Exodus, Numbers and Deuteronomy. Pointed and accentuated Hebrew text, with the Arabic translation of the Karaite Yeshu'ah ben 'Ari or al-Shaikh Abu 'l-Faraj Furḳan ibn Asad.</summary>
                     
                     
                     
